Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:19.11,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}同本應相遇的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.86,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}瘋狂地哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:25.95,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}願尋回那無法忘卻的愛　長相廝守
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.66,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}瘋狂吧{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}　Hey kids!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:31.49,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}就算如此未來也是虛幻的嗎{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.46,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}瘋狂吧{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}　Hey kids!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:39.50,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}放飛無聊的自我主義　毫無意義的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.13,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}瘋狂也沒關係嗎{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:44.65,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}不叫出我的名字嗎{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:46.93,opCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fscx86}{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}"I swear I respect the hero!!"
Comment: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:19.57,edJP,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.84,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}やがて巡り巡る季節に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.75,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}僕らは息をする
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.62,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}思い出になるその時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:50.44,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}ずっと忘れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:07.53,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}一人ぼっち膝を抱えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:10.45,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}見上げたんだ　あの日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:14.28,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}思ってたより晴れた空と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:16.72,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}あなたがそこにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:20.84,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}見えてるもの全て　胸に焼き付けたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.17,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}いつか来るさよならの時のため
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:27.50,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}だけど今は気づかぬふりをして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:33.08,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}僕は笑う　あなたと今
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:42.13,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}悲しみ　喜び　心臓の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:48.41,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}伝って動かすんだ　僕という命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:55.43,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}想いや感情　掛け値なしの愛を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:59.21,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}あなたがくれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:04.22,edJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}進むよ　見ててくれる？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.84,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}在循環往復的季節中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.75,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}我們盡情呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.62,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}已化為回憶的那個時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:50.44,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}也請你永遠不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:07.53,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}那一天我獨自環抱雙膝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:10.45,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:14.28,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}卻看到了比想像中還要晴朗的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:16.72,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}和你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:20.84,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}將能看到的東西都銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.17,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}為了總有一天將會到來的告別之時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:27.50,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}但如今我假裝沒有意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:33.08,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}綻放笑容　現在　和你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:42.13,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}悲傷　快樂　以及心臟的跳動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:48.41,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}將它們努力傳達　就是名為我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:55.43,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}戀慕　感情　以及無價的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:59.21,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}因為你給了我這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:04.22,edCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(300,300)}我才前進著　能看著我嗎{\fnFOT-TsukuMin Pr5N H\fs64\b0}？
